  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In `transferFrom` first receiver balance is increment and only then spender balance is decremented.\r\nThis allows to send more than you have. It is very minor as you send it to your self and total balance is not affected.\r\nHowever, it is inconsistent with `transfer` where you first decrements sender balance and only then increment receiver balance. \r\n",
